I won't forgive you.

00:37:44.000 --> 00:37:45.040
Who are you?

00:37:45.280 --> 00:37:46.280
Why did you tie me up?

00:37:47.280 --> 00:37:49.680
Miss Shangguan, calm down.

00:37:50.280 --> 00:37:52.400
Let me introduce myself.

00:37:52.840 --> 00:37:56.880
I’m Zhang Gong Yan, Division Commander of the Nationalist Party.

00:37:57.920 --> 00:37:58.960
Jang Gong-yeon.

00:38:00.720 --> 00:38:01.960
Are you Jang Gong-yeon?

00:38:02.800 --> 00:38:05.560
Ms. Shangguan seems to know me.

00:38:05.920 --> 00:38:06.960
Of course.

00:38:07.440 --> 00:38:08.680
Everyone knows you.

00:38:08.960 --> 00:38:12.240
The famous Division Commander Zhang Gong Yan

00:38:12.520 --> 00:38:14.120
indulged his men to bully the people.

00:38:14.400 --> 00:38:17.880
You look like a coward when you see the Japanese.

00:38:18.400 --> 00:38:19.560
Isn't that you?

00:38:21.080 --> 00:38:22.360
Miss Shangguan,

00:38:23.040 --> 00:38:24.440
Since you are a woman,

00:38:24.720 --> 00:38:27.760
I won't take this hearsay seriously.

00:38:28.560 --> 00:38:29.560
But I have to tell you

00:38:29.920 --> 00:38:31.680
you are in my hands now.

00:38:32.640 --> 00:38:33.800
You'd better behave.

00:38:34.240 --> 00:38:35.280
in case everyone is embarrassed.

00:38:35.480 --> 00:38:36.920
Do you know what embarrassment is?

00:38:38.120 --> 00:38:39.760
Since I'm here, I want to ask you

00:38:40.120 --> 00:38:42.360
why don't you fight the Japanese in real life?

00:38:42.720 --> 00:38:44.320
Because of people like you,

00:38:44.840 --> 00:38:46.240
the Japanese

00:38:46.520 --> 00:38:47.720
in our land.

00:39:04.400 --> 00:39:05.680
Miss Shangguan.

00:39:06.800 --> 00:39:08.240
I invited you here today

00:39:08.520 --> 00:39:10.040
to fight against Japan.

00:39:10.440 --> 00:39:11.440
I

00:39:11.840 --> 00:39:14.360
want to fight the Japanese.

00:39:14.600 --> 00:39:15.480
But

00:39:16.840 --> 00:39:18.960
His men are weak.

00:39:19.400 --> 00:39:20.480
It's hard to resist.

00:39:20.760 --> 00:39:22.480
The Japanese army

00:39:22.840 --> 00:39:24.640
So I sincerely invite

00:39:24.840 --> 00:39:27.320
Master Shangguan Bao, the head of Qinglong Fortress,

00:39:27.560 --> 00:39:29.040
led the swordsmen down the mountain

00:39:29.240 --> 00:39:30.720
and help me.

00:39:31.040 --> 00:39:33.520
Please do me a favor.

00:39:33.760 --> 00:39:35.040
Please make an exception.

00:39:35.720 --> 00:39:37.400
You can choose

00:39:37.840 --> 00:39:41.040
will be at your disposal.

00:39:41.320 --> 00:39:42.320
Dream on!

00:39:43.480 --> 00:39:45.160
My father would never

00:39:45.160 --> 00:39:46.080
like you.

00:39:46.680 --> 00:39:48.160
Release me now.

00:39:48.720 --> 00:39:50.400
Otherwise, my father will take his brothers

00:39:50.840 --> 00:39:52.400
with his men.

00:39:57.480 --> 00:40:00.320
Shangguan Bao is arrogant and arrogant.

00:40:00.800 --> 00:40:03.680
His daughter is also so arrogant.

00:40:04.800 --> 00:40:06.200
Let's see how long you can be arrogant.

00:40:06.440 --> 00:40:07.440
Cut the crap.

00:40:08.320 --> 00:40:09.640
Where did you lock my sister?

00:40:09.960 --> 00:40:10.720
Where's Ni?

00:40:11.000 --> 00:40:12.520
I've already

00:40:12.840 --> 00:40:14.320
the video.

00:40:14.680 --> 00:40:16.920
I just want her to tell Shangguan Bao

00:40:17.160 --> 00:40:19.040
if he doesn't surrender,

00:40:19.760 --> 00:40:21.760
I'll kill his precious daughter.

00:40:24.560 --> 00:40:25.480
Boss.

00:40:25.920 --> 00:40:28.240
do you need us to do something?

00:40:28.840 --> 00:40:30.160
Thank you for your kindness.

00:40:30.600 --> 00:40:32.360
This is my family matter.

00:40:32.760 --> 00:40:34.320
I won’t bother you.

00:40:36.840 --> 00:40:39.720
We'll leave you alone.

00:40:56.920 --> 00:40:57.760
Fly on the boat.

00:40:58.040 --> 00:40:58.800
Master,

00:41:01.360 --> 00:41:02.640
I have to go back to Qinglong Camp now.

00:41:02.840 --> 00:41:03.880
What happened, Master?

00:41:04.200 --> 00:41:05.160
Eagle ran away.

00:41:05.440 --> 00:41:06.320
I’ll go back with you.

00:41:06.520 --> 00:41:08.680
Maybe Madam needs help now.

00:41:09.320 --> 00:41:10.040
Fine.

00:41:10.320 --> 00:41:11.480
You and Eagle have always been close.

00:41:11.720 --> 00:41:13.160
Maybe I can help. Let's go.

00:41:20.440 --> 00:41:21.080
Sister.

00:41:21.400 --> 00:41:24.240
My sister was taken to Jang Gong-yeon's command center.

00:41:24.680 --> 00:41:26.680
They asked me to tell you

00:41:27.160 --> 00:41:29.400
and ask you to surrender.

00:41:29.760 --> 00:41:30.400
Otherwise,

00:41:31.280 --> 00:41:33.800
Or they'll kill you.

00:41:34.840 --> 00:41:35.880
Okay.

00:41:36.840 --> 00:41:37.400
Don't cry.

00:41:37.560 --> 00:41:38.680
Sorry, sir.

00:41:39.960 --> 00:41:40.960
It's all my fault.

00:41:41.200 --> 00:41:43.160
I shouldn't have let her go down the mountain.

00:41:43.640 --> 00:41:45.400
Please save her.

00:41:46.240 --> 00:41:47.760
Take her down to rest.

00:41:48.080 --> 00:41:48.680
Yes.

00:41:49.760 --> 00:41:50.120
Sister.

00:41:50.320 --> 00:41:51.160
Let's go, Miss He.

00:41:51.720 --> 00:41:52.920
Sir, please save my sister. Let's go down first.

00:41:53.200 --> 00:41:53.600
Miss He.

00:41:53.920 --> 00:41:54.760
Sir.

00:41:57.840 --> 00:41:58.800
Hurry up.

00:42:00.840 --> 00:42:02.400
Qinglong Fortress is lively.

00:42:03.720 --> 00:42:04.360
Looks like

00:42:04.520 --> 00:42:07.080
Wu Zhen really pissed Shangguan Bao off.

00:42:11.480 --> 00:42:12.360
Why are you laughing?

00:42:13.320 --> 00:42:14.320
Did I smile?

00:42:14.800 --> 00:42:15.760
You didn't?

00:42:18.960 --> 00:42:20.560
Actually, this is a good thing

00:42:20.840 --> 00:42:21.920
for us.

00:42:22.840 --> 00:42:24.440
It's a good timing.

00:42:25.560 --> 00:42:27.360
But it's a problem.

00:42:28.080 --> 00:42:30.320
Shangguan Bao has always hated

00:42:30.480 --> 00:42:31.840
of Jang Gong Yeon.

00:42:32.200 --> 00:42:34.160
Even if he doesn't cooperate with the Communist Party,

00:42:35.120 --> 00:42:36.120
and cooperate with us,

00:42:37.880 --> 00:42:38.520
to work with us.

00:42:38.720 --> 00:42:40.680
Shangguan Bao is not a fool.

00:42:41.200 --> 00:42:42.200
How can the fortress be quiet

00:42:42.440 --> 00:42:44.360
How can the fortress be quiet?

00:42:45.240 --> 00:42:46.600
When the time is right,

00:42:46.920 --> 00:42:48.440
he will definitely see the situation

00:42:48.720 --> 00:42:49.840
and make a choice.

